{"id": "anc_split_resize", "modality": "animations", "name": "Split Resize", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS, NO <canvas>) of a two-pane split view (left list pane, right detail pane) with a vertical divider. Over ~3s the divider slides from 30% to 60% of the width and back, resizing both panes; each pane's content reflows to fit. Panes always fill the full width together with no gap or overlap, and content never overflows its pane.", "requirements": ["The two panes together fill the full viewport width with no gap and no overlap at every frame", "The divider's x-position changes over time (the split ratio animates)", "Both panes stay fully within the viewport (nothing clipped at the screen edges)", "Each pane's content stays inside that pane (no text overflow across the divider)", "The divider stays vertical and spans the full height between the panes", "No horizontal scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3361, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 3490}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 7, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3093, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 16257}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 5, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3660, "rv_n_defects": 15, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 19791}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_split_resize_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_split_resize_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Animated Split Pane</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            overflow: hidden;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .left-pane {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            box-shadow: 2px 0 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            animation: leftPaneResize 6s ease-in-out infinite;\n        }\n\n        .right-pane {\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            flex: 1;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .divider {\n            width: 4px;\n            background: #4a90e2;\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            height: 100%;\n            z-index: 3;\n            cursor: col-resize;\n            animation: dividerMove 6s ease-in-out infinite;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .divider::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: -8px;\n            top: 50%;\n            transform: translateY(-50%);\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 60px;\n            background: #4a90e2;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .pane-header {\n            padding: 32px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4a90e2, #357abd);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .pane-title {\n     